The observed enhancement in the photocurrent (Jph) can be understood in terms of enhanced generation rate (G) and separation capability of photoinduced charge carriers which in turn depends upon the width of the depletion region (W) at the CoFe2O4/electrolyte interface and is given by the following relationship5;1Jph~qGW\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
